data.description: This stunning two-story home nestled on a quiet tree-lined street in Enchanted Forest is a testament to timeless elegance and classic contemporary design. The exteriors white-washed facade with contrasting black metal mansard roof line, sets the tone for the exquisite interiors within.This 1892 sq ft. layout is boasting with three spacious bedrooms and two luxurious bathrooms. The home is adorned with modern, imported tile on the main level lending a cool and inviting ambiance to every room. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the open galley kitchen,  soft tone cabinetry and oversized decorative pulls add a touch of opulence. The open floor-plan seamlessly integrates the kitchen with the family room & dining room. The primary bedroom is a sanctuary of tranquility, complete with a spa like bathroom and a very generously sized walk-in closet. Every detail of the home has been chosen to create a harmonious blend of style and comfort. Located near Wurzbach Pkwy & 281, this home offers unparalleled convenience. A home that truly stands out for its aesthetic appeal, thoughtful design and quality craftsmanship, a perfect balance of comfort luxury and convenience.
